  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK184">
<l>kaṇṇiṉṟu kaṇṇaṟac colliṉuñ collaṟka</l>
<l>muṉṉiṉṟu piṉṉōkkāc col</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though you speak without kindness before another's face speak not in his absence words which regard not the evil subsequently resulting from it.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
